name: The Domestic Enchantress
text: Love this little Pizza Hut express, I go here occasionally to get thier breadsticks with extra cheese on them when I'm craving it. The prices are reasonable and it's nice to have a Pizza Hut that's close to Marine City

name: Jacklynn Gibson
text: Love the variety of food you can get. Ribs are my favorite !

text: Breadsticks are good. Pizza is eh.

text: Best food out in the county.
